flowchart TD
    Player -->|types guess| UI

    subgraph UI ["app.py — Streamlit UI"]
        Sidebar["Sidebar\n(difficulty, range, attempts)"]
        Input["Text Input\n(raw guess)"]
        Buttons["Buttons\n(Submit / New Game)"]
        Display["Display\n(hint, score, status)"]
        Debug["Debug Panel\n(secret, history)"]
    end

    subgraph State ["st.session_state"]
        secret
        attempts
        score
        status
        history
        difficulty
    end

    subgraph Logic ["logic_utils.py — Pure Game Logic"]
        get_range["get_range_for_difficulty(difficulty)\nReturns (low, high)"]
        parse["parse_guess(raw)\nReturns (success, int, error)"]
        check["check_guess(guess, secret)\nReturns (outcome, hint)"]
        update["update_score(score, outcome, attempt)\nReturns new score"]
    end

    Sidebar -->|difficulty| get_range
    get_range -->|low, high| Sidebar
    get_range -->|low, high| Input

    Buttons -->|Submit| parse
    parse -->|valid int| check
    check -->|outcome, hint| Display
    check -->|outcome| update
    update -->|new score| State

    Buttons -->|New Game| State
    State -->|persists across reruns| UI
